    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it\u2019s been kept in a garage its whole life. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. You really have to see it in person to believe how clean it is! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
